-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/Lu%E1%BA%ADn-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-NhSvboFHPG8xzvZO1CQzGw">Luận thi kỳ 04 - 論詩其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/Phi%E1%BA%BFm-%C3%A1i-ch%C3%BAng/poem-vRbxRLFOPBjm83wKLfI8Qw">Phiếm ái chúng - 泛愛眾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Vu-s%C6%A1n-cao/poem-59jjQdJQeJNH1JYIRTGRtA">Vu sơn cao - 巫山高</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
